nodes.text: Tepra Tseelit was a lieutenant in the Alliance to Restore the Republic who served in the Tatooine Patrol.

Sometime during the Galactic Civil War, the Tatooine Patrol discovered Slave I, the personal starship of Boba Fett, abandoned geosynchronous orbit of the planet Tatooine. Lieutenant Tepra Tseelit, with Captain Noan Jeraddi, wrote Incident Report 39:3:22 detailing what happened to Slave I and the blast-proof strongbox found in the cockpit.
